Expression data (m genes × n samples) were scaled such that each gene had a mean expression of 0 and standard deviation of 1. The scaled expression matrix, X, was then factored by SVD:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
