For qRT-PCR, RNA was extracted from the purified cell populations using the RNeasy micro kit (Qiagen), then converted to first strand complementary DNA using Superscript III reverse transcriptase (Invitrogen). Quantitative PCR was performed on a BioRad C1000 Thermal Cycler with a CFX96 Real Time PCR Detection System using SYBR Green Master Mix (Invitrogen). Fold expression change was calculated using a variant of the \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
